                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920329-43-off240 t17920329-43-cd241"></join>, and putting him in fear, and feloniously taking from his person and against his will, one cotton gown, value 20 s. and one linen shift, value 5 s.
